sp_css.css:
/* Use this stylesheet for Tasker Modal widgets such as:
Tasker Modal - Delete Task
Tasker Modal - Reopen Tasks
Tasker Modal - Response Comments

The widget will find the CSS in a auto filled <style> tag.

2.7.0 | 2021-08-29 | mmcc | STRY0107404 - Draft Scheduled Tasks – UI – Delete Modal 
Put into a style sheet
2.7.0 | 2021-09-03 | mmcc | DFCT0010476 - "Acknowledgement Prompt" does not have an "Acknowledge" button so users cannot use Tasker
Dropped class modal-footer; Added class .dtech-modal-widget-body
Change class dtech-modal-footer to dtech-modal-widget-footer and updated to have padding-top to reduce white space and position 
since body sets it as well
2.7.0 | 2021-09-14 | mmcc | STRY0099532 - DIA- 'Mass Reopen' Task Tree Modal (MVP)
Renamed to be more generic
Added vertical align for the radio button label 
Changed $tasker-delete-prompt-perm-delete to use $tasker-modal-prompt-standard-text-color
Changed CSS Selector .dtech-perm-delete to use .dtech-standard-text-color
2.7.0 | 2021-09-22 | mmcc | STRY0108861 - DIA- Cancel from Top Task Notification 
Added CSS Selector asterisk
2.7.2 | 2021-12-27 | mmcc | DFCT0010728 - Modal Scheduled Tasks shows title data with an ellipsis
Some CSS selectors will be found in Tasker Overall Style Sheet
2.8 | 2022-02-02 | mmcc | STRY0117772 - Tech Debt - Identify Style Sheets when viewed from browser Dev Tools
Added .TaskerModalPromptWidgetsStyleSheet to name which style sheet this is when viewed from browser Dev Tools
2.8.1 | 2023-04-19 | mmcc | STRY0135713 - Modal showing all comments when clicking the Response Column
Added .dtech-modal-widget-override-modal-body-pad, .dtech-modal-widget-container-outer
.dtech-modal-widget-response-container, .dtech-modal-widget-text-black-bold and
.dtech-sonic-silver-text-color
*/
.TaskerModalPromptWidgetsStyleSheet { display: none; } /* Name of Style Sheet, do not use to style HTML */


.asterisk::before {
  color: $brand-danger;
  content: "*";
  position: absolute;
  margin-left: -1%;
}

label.dtech-radio-inline {
  vertical-align: middle;
}

/* this was a copy of Bootstrap's modal-body */
.dtech-modal-widget-body {
  padding: 15px;
  position: relative;
}

/* Use this CSS selector in any Tasker modal that needs to override padding on OOTB CSS selector modal-body */
.dtech-modal-widget-override-modal-body-pad {
  margin:-5px -15px;
}

/* Use this CSS selector in any Tasker modal that needs a Bootstrap container for rows with left/right padding of 5px */
.dtech-modal-widget-container-outer {
  padding: 0 20px;
}

/* Use this CSS selector in the Tasker Modal - Response Comments html for the response comments to be scrollable */
.dtech-modal-widget-response-container {
  flex-grow: 1;
  max-height: calc(100vh - 55vh);
  overflow: auto;
  /* padding-right: 5px; */
}

/* this was a copy of Bootstrap's modal-footer */
.dtech-modal-widget-footer {
  /* padding: 15px; */
  padding-top: 15px;
  text-align: right;
  border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  /* added position */
  position: relative;
}

.dtech-modal-widget-text-black-bold {
  color: black;
  font-weight: bold;
}

h1 {
  color: $tasker-color-brown-red;
}

.dtech-task-name {
  color: $tasker-delete-prompt-task-name;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

.dtech-standard-text-color {
  color: $tasker-modal-prompt-standard-text-color;
}

.dtech-sonic-silver-text-color {
  color: $tasker-color-gray-sonic-silver;
}

.dtech-sonic-silver-text-italic {
  color: $tasker-color-gray-sonic-silver;
  font-style: italic;
}

.dtech-subtasks-also-deleted {
  color: $tasker-delete-prompt-subtasks-also-deleted;
  margin-left: 5px;
}
